      <title>奥地利极右翼领导人获授权组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/austrian-far-right-leader-receives-mandate-to-form-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利极右翼领导人赫伯特·基克尔获得总统亚历山大·范德贝伦的授权组建政府，这使得自由党领袖距离成为总理又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/austrian-far-right-leader-receives-mandate-to-form-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 将竞业禁止期延长至 21 个月以留住人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/citadel-extends-non-compete-to-21-months-to-retain-talent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 的 Citadel 将部分投资组合经理的竞业禁止协议延长至 21 个月，凸显了多策略对冲基金之间持续不断的招聘战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/citadel-extends-non-compete-to-21-months-to-retain-talent</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁和美国钢铁公司在拜登阻挠交易后提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/nippon-steel-us-steel-file-lawsuits-in-move-to-keep-deal-alive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司和美国钢铁公司联合提起诉讼，为维护两家公司的合并计划做最后的努力，但该合并计划上周遭到总统乔·拜登的阻止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/nippon-steel-us-steel-file-lawsuits-in-move-to-keep-deal-alive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:18:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将限制关税 报告称美元两月内最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场押注美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税计划不会像最初担心的那样广泛且会引发通胀，美元兑大多数主要货币周一大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国债券收益率在 1190 亿美元债券发售前创下 14 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-30-year-bond-yield-hits-highest-since-2023-ahead-of-auctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于动荡的美国国债市场准备本周发行 1190 亿美元的新政府债券，美国 30 年期债券收益率攀升至 2023 年底以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-30-year-bond-yield-hits-highest-since-2023-ahead-of-auctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 08:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯计划进一步大举借贷以支付大型项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudi-arabia-plans-37-billion-borrowing-spree-to-pay-for-huge-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯是去年新兴市场中最大的债券发行国之一，随着该国推动其庞大的经济转型计划，该国在 2025 年开始大举融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudi-arabia-plans-37-billion-borrowing-spree-to-pay-for-huge-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 08:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称特朗普可能削减关税计划，铜价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华盛顿邮报》报道称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的助手正在研究适用于每个国家但仅涵盖主要商品进口的关税计划，此后，伦敦铜价上涨逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:59:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Paychex 正在洽谈收购规模较小的竞争对手 Paycor</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/paychex-is-said-to-be-in-talks-to-buy-smaller-rival-paycor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Paychex Inc. 正在就收购薪资处理领域规模较小的竞争对手 Paycor HCM Inc. 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/paychex-is-said-to-be-in-talks-to-buy-smaller-rival-paycor</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 23:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元回落，科技股上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，科技公司领涨股市，由于人们对人工智能基础设施的持续需求重拾信心，股市进一步摆脱年底低迷。美元跌幅创 11 月以来最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
